# 3. Current Ground Truth

## 3.1. L1-L5 Legal Dossier

The L1-L5 from `docs/specs/Tài Liệu Xuất Bản/na/natt_os_nhom_1_ho_so_nen_tang_ky_thuat_v_1 (4).md` are legal/publication dossier layers:

```text
L1 = Capability Profile
L2 = Technology Whitepaper
L3 = IP Dossier / Hồ sơ SHTT
L4 = Trademark Dossier
L5 = Copyright Source Code Record
```

This L1-L5 set is not the same as Kernel Nauion 7 concentric layers.

## 3.2. Kernel Nauion

Kernel Nauion remains the 7-layer grammar / kernel map:

```text
L1 Identity Root
L2 Boundary Shell
L3 State / Memory
L4 Protection Spectrum
L5 Encoding / Transport / Surface Signal
L6 Expression / Render / UI
L7 Seal / SiraSign / Audit Boundary
```

Do not confuse:
- Legal L1-L5 = publication/legal dossier.
- Kernel L1-L7 = grammar / structure.
- Materialization 4 phases = spec/design → manifest/schema → scanner/rule → git/adoption.

## 3.3. Hardware Field

